trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder"></xref> Web server control.
Extend the ContentPlaceHolderDesigner class if you want to create a designer for a class that extends the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolder> control.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ContentPlaceHolderDesigner"></xref> class.
Gets a value indicating whether the control can be resized.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control can be resized; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets the HTML that is used to represent the control at design time.
The HTML markup used to represent the control at design time.
The root component is not a <xref href="System.Web.UI.MasterPage"></xref> instance.
Gets the HTML that is used to represent the control at design time using the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> object.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> object containing the regions to use for generating design-time HTML.
The HTML that is used to represent the control at design time.
The root component is not a <xref href="System.Web.UI.MasterPage"></xref> instance.
Gets the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object from which to extract content.
The content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object.
Gets the persistable inner HTML of the control.
The persistable inner HTML of the control.
Sets the content of the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> object.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> instance to set.
The new content for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref>.
